      "content": "but it's not just about peace in the quiet moments. the darkness is heavy. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the pressure is to just... stop fighting it. like, if there's nothing there, why am i still trying to keep the lights on? it feels like there's no point in even trying to stay in the fight when the void is just waiting anyway.",
